44 struct Attribute {
45  Namespace xmlns;
46  Namespace prefix;
47  AttributeName name;
48  AttributeValue value;
49  operator std::string() const { return value; };
50  operator bool() const { return (value == "true"); };
51  operator int() const { return std::stoi(value); };
52  operator double() const { return std::stod(value); };
53  Attribute& operator=(const std::string& s) { value = s; return *this; };
54  Attribute& operator=(const bool& b) { value = (b ? "true" : "false"); return *this; };
55  Attribute& operator=(const int& i) { value = std::to_string(i); return *this; };
56  Attribute& operator=(const double& d) { value = std::to_string(d); return *this; };
57 };

150  void findRecursive(std::vector<std::reference_wrapper<T> >& result, const Children& descendants)
151  {
152  for (auto& descendant : descendants) {
